      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――芽衣との散歩中",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――While out on a walk with Mei",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり！　見て見てあそこのモニター！\nサニピの映像だ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I knew it! Look at that screen there!\nIt’s footage of Sunny Peace!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.1666666684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 8.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "この間のライブバトルだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Taken from the recent live battle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "振り付けがかなり難しいって\n怜ちゃん燃えてたっけな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The steps were pretty hard.\nSo Rei-chan was really getting into it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 16.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん！\n小さい女の子が楽しそうに見てる！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}-san!\nThat little girl is loving it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 22.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "夢中で見てるよ～\nはぁぁ～……か～わいいな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s completely captivated!\nHehe. How cute!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 31.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "見て見て！\n画面に向かっておてて振ってる～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look‚ look!\nShe’s waving at the screen!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 35.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あんな風に喜んでくれるのは嬉しいな\n……ん？　どうしたんだ、芽衣？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seeing that kind of thing makes me happy too.\n…Huh? Mei‚ what’s up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 42.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "あの子、怜ちゃんのダンスソロの時だけ\nピタッて止まってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s completely stopped‚ but look.\nOnly for Rei-chan’s dance solo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 48.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "興味がないのか……いや、違うな\n目が凄くキラキラしてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe she’s not interested… no‚ that’s not it.\nHer eyes are sparkling.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 55.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "あんな小さい子にも\n怜ちゃんのダンスの凄さは分かるんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even a little kid like that\ncan see how incredible Rei-chan’s dancing is.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 60.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "そっか、そうだよね\n怜ちゃんのダンスを実際に見てもらえば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s it. That’s the answer!\nHe just has to see Rei-chan actually dancing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 70.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "よーし、決めた！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That settles it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 74.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、芽衣はもう大丈夫\n帰ろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m good now‚ {user}-san. Good to go.\nLet’s go back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それは構わないけど……随分すっきりした\n顔をしてるな。一体何を決めたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whatever you say. You look a lot more\ncheerful too. What did you settle‚ exactly?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 85.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "いいからいいから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Later‚ later~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "積もる話は事務所でってことで～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We can get down to business back at the office.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 92.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それで、これからどうするつもりなんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay. So what’s your plan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "まずは芽衣の気持ちから話すね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First‚ let Mei tell you how Mei's feeling.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ね、怜ちゃんがお家で練習しているのを\n覗いてた時から……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since that first time Mei peeked at Rei-chan\ntraining infront of her house…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんのダンスが大好きなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been in love with her dancing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "本当にかっこいいし\n一緒に練習してるといっつも見とれちゃうんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She really is so cool.\nI can’t take my eyes off her‚ even when I’m dancing too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-mei018.m4a",
      "text": "それにそれに、怜ちゃんて凄く頑張るでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then you have how hard Rei-chan works. Her commitment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-mei019.m4a",
      "text": "練習で「これくらいでいいかなー」って思った時も\n怜ちゃんを見るともうひと頑張り出来るの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Every time I think “that’s enough for today‚”\nI look over at Rei-chan and she gives me the boost I need!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-mei020.m4a",
      "text": "同じステージに立つ仲間だけど……\n芽衣は怜ちゃんの一番のファンかも！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know we sing and dance on the same stage‚\nbut I think I’m probably Rei-chan’s biggest fan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣……怜のことをそんな風に思ってたのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei… So that’s how you feel about Rei-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_03_02-mei021.m4a",
      "text": "それに、さっきの女の子を見たでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You saw that little girl too‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
